RideSummary.Title: MPSantaBarbara
RideSummary.Comment: To Zuma first then to Carpenteria.  Felt good even with the distance.  Ate bacon and Cream of Wheat for breakfast and had two water bottles with 6 scoops each Perpetuem.  Flat tire near Magu Rock on return.
